4.PROBLEM : 268. Missing Number
SOURCE CODE : 
        class Solution {
            public int missingNumber(int[] nums) {
                int n=nums.length;
                int actualSum=Arrays.stream(nums).sum();
                int expectSum=n*(n+1)/2;
                return expectSum-actualSum;
            }
        }
